Name: King of Lineland
Summary: The King of Lineland is the entity ruling the one dimensional world. He is the longest line segment, and presumably the strongest, being 6.457 inches long. He spends his time flirting and showing off to the 2 female line segments to his left and right. When he is encountered by A Square, he responds in violence, fear, and outrage.
